  "detailed_description": "Glide through a breathtaking alpine scape in the search of an answer as to why this is your only memory.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTHE LAST SCAPE can be played with gamepad or simply with the mouse, the controls are easy for a comfortable experience. The game can be enjoyed by anyone regardless of their age.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFor this unique soul simulator, LIDAR laser scan data is used in its raw point cloud form, rendering millions of points in real-time from a dataset of more than one billion 3D points that accurately depict the real world.",
  "about_the_game": "Glide through a breathtaking alpine scape in the search of an answer as to why this is your only memory.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTHE LAST SCAPE can be played with gamepad or simply with the mouse, the controls are easy for a comfortable experience. The game can be enjoyed by anyone regardless of their age.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFor this unique soul simulator, LIDAR laser scan data is used in its raw point cloud form, rendering millions of points in real-time from a dataset of more than one billion 3D points that accurately depict the real world.",
